author: MIRIAM and MANOEL CHAVES
title: MIRIAM and MANOEL CHAVES
text:
I have my sailboat for 13 years in Europe.
The experience exchanged with Yacht Registration Holland was very important for me. I suggest everyone looking for a simple and straight forward register procedure to talk to them.
